<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Rothenburg ob der Tauber</head><p>Der Rat bittet um eine Verlängerung des Waffenstillstands zwischen den Adressaten und dem Deutschorden bis Jakobstag und Teilnahme an einem Gerichtstag zu Nürnberg am kommenden Sonntag.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_471" id="234v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_471_r1l18">Den von Rotemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_471_r1l19"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> wır <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> von den vvırdıgen ~ dem <expan>Com<ex>m</ex>enteẅr</expan> bey vns vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l20"><expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Com<ex>m</ex>enteẅrn</expan> deẅtſchs Ordens <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . wıe daʒ etwas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l22"><expan>vnwılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Jı </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_471_r1l21">etlıchen ırs ordens </ab></add> vnd ewr ſey / von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe ſıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l23">ergangen haben / <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſache bıs auf nu ſand <expan>Joh<ex>anns</ex></expan> tag <expan>ſünwente<ex>n</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l24">in gut angeſtellt ſeyn / Wan wır nu <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teıls <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſeͣhen daʒ dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l25">ſache <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex>ſeıt</expan> mıt <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l26">ſo <expan>bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> . dıe ſache in gut anſteen ʒu laſſen bıs auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l27">ſand Jacobs tag ſchıerıſt in maſſ als es auf ſand Johanns tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l28">angeſtellet ıſt / vnd daʒ Jr <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l29">vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> wellet von nu ſunntag v̈ber viij tag . ſo </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_472" id="235r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_472_r2l1"><expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darʒu <expan>dıene<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd fürderlıch ſein Ob dıe ſache mıt freẅnt = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_472_r2l2">ſchaft abgeen mug / Vnd was <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darinn well ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_472_r2l3">das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbt</expan> vns bey dıſem <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_471" id="234v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Rotemburg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> von den wirdigen,
                                                dem <expan>com<ex>m</ex>entewr</expan> bey uns und
                                                  <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>com<ex>m</ex>entewrn</expan> dewtschs ordens
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie daz etwas
                                                  <expan>unwille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>etlichen irs ordens</add> und ewr sey von
                                                  <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die sich ergangen
                                                haben, <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sache bis auf
                                                nu <app>
<note><q type="date">sand
                                                  <expan>Joh<ex>anns</ex></expan> tag
                                                  <expan>sünwente<ex>n</ex></expan> schierist
                                                  </q>24.06.1422</note>
</app> in gut angestellt seyn. Wan wir nu
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teils
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> seͣhen, daz die sache
                                                  <expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>beid<ex>er</ex>seit</expan> mit
                                                  <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so
                                                  <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                                  <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>, die sache in gut
                                                ansteen zu lassen bis auf <app>
<note><q type="date">sand Jacobs tag
                                                  schierist</q>25.07.1422</note>
</app> in mass, als es auf sand Johanns tag
                                                angestellet ist, und daz ir
                                                  <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu
                                                  <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag zu uns
                                                  <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> wellet, von nu <app>
<note><q type="date">sunntag über viii tag</q>28.06.1422</note>
</app>. So <pb facs="#facs_472" id="235r"/>
<expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darzu
                                                  <expan>diene<ex>n</ex></expan> und fürderlich
                                                sein, ob die sache mit frewntschaft abgeen mug; und
                                                was <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darinn well sein,
                                                das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibt</expan> uns bey
                                                disem <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
